short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Call Integration for Dynamix's Global UC Voice

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Dynamix for Chrome brings your Dynamix phone system to your Chrome browser. Easily place calls with one click from your browser and take the call anywhere and on any device you want.

Now supports CRM integration and call logging.
